## 🚀 About the Project

This is my personal **portfolio website** built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  
It showcases my skills, projects, and contact information in a clean, responsive, and modern design.

The goal of this project is to present myself professionally as a developer and make it easy for recruiters or clients to learn about my work.

---

## 📁 Project Structure

Portfolio-Website/
│
├── assets/        # Images, icons, and media files
├── css/           # Stylesheets
├── js/            # JavaScript files
├── CNAME          # Custom domain configuration (GitHub Pages)
└── index.html     # Main landing page

---

## ✨ Features

- 📱 Fully responsive design (mobile, tablet, desktop)
- 🎨 Modern and clean UI/UX
- ⚡ Fast loading static website
- 🧭 Smooth scrolling navigation
- 🧑 About Me section
- 💼 Projects showcase section
- 🛠 Skills display section
- 📬 Contact section
- 🌐 Hosted using GitHub Pages

---

## 🛠️ Built With

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla JS)
- GitHub Pages

